Kodanuki
========

This repository contains the kodanuki game engine and my upcoming game with
the same name. It is simply a toy project to learn more about game engine's.
Currently the kodanuki engine is primarily developed for GNU/Linux using C++.

Dependencies
------------

- gcc
- glfw
- make
- ninja
- python
- vulkan
- optional: doctest
- optional: pygount
- optional: valgrind
